  <bioghist id="aspace_958cd7de8794cb953cfc05ec0b313965">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>Tompkins County AIDS Task Force formed in late 1985 to mobilize a countywide response to the AIDS epidemic. In late 1988 the name changed to AIDSWORK: HIV Support and Information for Tompkins County.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_bfc5e4fb3f1c5702d4efb2a59332d89c">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Meeting minutes, budgets, grant proposals, broadsides, and some correspondence from Tompkins County AIDS Task Force and AIDS Work; also subject files, office files, material from other AIDS organizations, photographs, and other material. Posters that duplicated ones in collection #51-1-2746 were removed. A list of these posters is provided at the end of the guide.</p>  </scopecontent>
